About Us
The Whole Enchilada Has Been Keepin’ It Fresh Since 2006 And Was Conceptualized By Two Local Brothers With Taste For Tacos And A Hankering For Hot Sauce. We Have Been Taking The Burrito Business By Storm With Our Unique Blend Of "Classic With A Twist" Menu Favorites Enjoyed Amongst A Hip And Trendy Atmosphere. Promising A Fun And Friendly Dining Experience For Customers And Connoisseurs Alike, Guests Of TWE Can Enjoy An Ambience Of Personality, Wit And "Cutting Edge" Charisma While Choosing From A Selection Of Simple, Yet Savory, "No Frills" Fresh Mex. We Look Forward To Hosting You Soon!
